د العزيز(@)(@)(@@) - قراءة في ديوان شيخ الصوفية باليمن عبد الهادي السودي ، مجلة دراسات يمنية ، ع 43 سنة 1991م.(@)(@)(@@) - تقرير دراسات الهيئة العامة للآثار في الجمهورية اليمنية ، مكتب آثار لحج لسنة 1997م.(@)(@)(@@) المراجع الأجنبية(@)(@)(@@) - Butler (H.C).(@)(@)(@@) ... Architecture and other . Arts. Newyork, 1930.(@)(@)(@@) - Cossonnet, Nahida, et Solang .(@)(@)(@@) ... Les Inscription la Mosqee, de Dibim, Paris, 1996.(@)(@)(@@) - Creswell ( K.A.C.)(@)(@)(@@) ... Early Muslim Architecture. Oxford, 1932(@)(@)(@@) ... The Muslim Architecture of Egypt. Oxford, 1952.(@)(@)(@@) ... A Short Account of Early Muslim Architecture London, 1958.(@)(@)(@@) - Elbasha, Hassan.(@)(@)(@@) ... The Muqarnas. Manbar Al Islam. Vol. V. No. 1.(@)(@)(@@) Finster Barbara.(@)(@)(@@) ... Archaologische. Berichete Aus Dem Yemmen , Band 111.(@)(@)(@@) - Flury, Samual.(@)(@)(@@) ... Die. Or nament der Hakim und Azahar Moschee , Heidelberg, 1912.(@)(@)(@@) - Galvin, Lucien.(@)(@)(@@) ... Thula, Architecture et. Urbanism, Paris, 1984.(@)(@)PageV01P355(@)(@)(@@) - Herzfeld, Ernst.(@)(@)(@@) ... Damascus, Studies in Architecture. Ars Islamic, IX. 1942.(@)(@)(@@) - Hirshi, Susanne et Max.(@)(@)(@@) ... L’Architecture Au Yemen Du Nord.(@)(@)(@@) - Lewcok. (R).(@)(@)(@@) ... Three Medieval Mosques in the Yemen Oriental Art Vol XX no 2 1974.(@)(@)(@@) - Makki, Shohd.(@)(@)(@@) ... Les Ecoles Rassulides Ataiz. Memire de D.E.A. 1995.(@)(@)(@@) - Monneret, de Villard.(@)(@)(@@) La Necropoli Musulmana di Aswan La Caire, 1930.(@)(@)(@@) - Musil.(@)(@)(@@) ... The middle Euphrates. NewYork, 1927.(@)(@)(@@) - Sauvaget, Jean.(@)(@)(@@) ... La’ Mosque Omeyyad, Madine.(@)(@)(@@) - Serjent, R.B.(@)(@)(@@) ... Mihrab, Bulletione of School of orient and African Studies, Vol, XXII Paris, 1959(@)(@)(@@) ... Sanna An Arabian Islamic City, London, 1983.(@)(@)(@@) - Wiet & Hauteceur.(@)(@)(@@) ... La Mosquees du Caire, 1858.م(@)(@)(@@) قائمة الأشكال واللوحات :(@)(@)(@@) أولا : الأشكال(@)(@)(@@) شكل (1( مسقط أفقي لضري